## ZEC ##

## Help
./zcash-cli help

## balance
./zcash-cli getbalance

## picks one of the generated addresses that haven't received coin
./zcash-cli getnewaddress

## Show transactions that have received cash 
./zcash-cli listreceivedbyaddress 0 true

## Send transactions
./zcash-cli sendtoaddress <taddress> 0.7

## List transactions to wallets
./zcash-cli listtransactions | grep to:
